 with CIRTL are available and worth your time to investigate. Welcome and we’re excited to know and help you.','Students & Postdocs','','inherit','closed','open','','20-autosave-v1','','','2015-08-20 02:57:34','2015-08-20 02:57:34','',20,'www.celt-staging.com2015/08/01/20-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(30,1,'2015-08-01 22:43:55','2015-08-01 22:43:55','','Teaching','','inherit','closed','open','','16-autosave-v1','','','2015-08-01 22:43:55','2015-08-01 22:43:55','',16,'www.celt-staging.com2015/08/01/16-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2015-08-05 17:19:15','2015-08-05 17:19:15','','Students & Postdocs','','inherit','closed','open','','20-revision-v1','','','2015-08-05 17:19:15','2015-08-05 17:19:15','',20,'www.celt-staging.com2015/08/05/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(32,1,'2015-08-05 17:31:28','2015-08-05 17:31:28','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Preparing Future Faculty (PFF) program supplements departmental graduate preparation by offering additional teaching, mentoring, and learning possibilities. These enriching experiences help prepare postdoctoral fellows, Ph.D. students, and master’s students for an academic career and provide further credentialing to be competitive on the academic job market. The overarching goal of PFF is to better prepare graduate students and post docs for faculty careers at a variety of institutions through a combination of seminars, mentoring, and practical classroom and departmental service experiences. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The following sections provide more information about the program and how to participate.</span></p>','Preparing Future Faculty','The Preparing Future Faculty (PFF) program supplements departmental graduate preparation by offering additional teaching, mentoring, and learning possibilities. ','publish','closed','open','','preparing-future-faculty','','','2015-11-15 20:47:41','2015-11-15 20:47:41','',20,'www.celt-staging.com?page_id=32',0,'page','',0),(33,1,'2015-08-0